{"surah_number":112,"arabic":" الاخلاص","latin":"Al-Ikhlāṣ","transliteration":"Al-Ikhlas","translation":"Ikhlas","total_ayat":4,"location":"Makkiyah","ayat":[{"surah_number":112,"ayat_number":1,"arabic":"قُلْ هُوَ اللّٰهُ اَحَدٌۚ","kitabah":"قُلْ هُوَ اللّٰهُ اَحَدٌۚ","latin":"Qul huwallāhu aḥad(un).","translation":"Katakanlah (Nabi Muhammad), “Dialah Allah Yang Maha Esa."},{"surah_number":112,"ayat_number":2,"arabic":"اَللّٰهُ الصَّمَدُۚ","kitabah":"اَللّٰهُ الصَّمَدُۚ","latin":"Allāhuṣ-ṣamad(u).","translation":"Allah tempat meminta segala sesuatu."},{"surah_number":112,"ayat_number":3,"arabic":"لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُوْلَدْۙ","kitabah":"لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُوْلَدْۙ","latin":"Lam yalid wa lam yūlad.","translation":"Dia tidak beranak dan tidak pula diperanakkan"},{"surah_number":112,"ayat_number":4,"arabic":"وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَّهٗ كُفُوًا اَحَدٌ ࣖ","kitabah":"وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَّهٗ كُفُوًا اَحَدٌ ࣖ","latin":"Wa lam yakul lahū kufuwan aḥad(un).","translation":"serta tidak ada sesuatu pun yang setara dengan-Nya.”"}]}